This video showcases ResumePulse, an AI-powered web app built during the “GenAI-Powered Solutions: Hack The Matrix” hackathon. The app allows users to upload PDF resumes and optionally add a job description, then instantly provides:

> Keyword & skills extraction

> ATS match percentage

> Resume rating (clarity, impact, ATS readiness)

> Line-level improvement suggestions

> Missing skills detection

> AI-generated 2-line professional summary
